Changes in @NEW@
================

New Features
------------
* The Update Service now utilizes Conary 2.0.
* Configuration is now stored in a config.d-style directory for added
  flexibility.
* The repository can now be switched to PostgreSQL via a plugin in the
  administration interface.
* The backup plugin is now enabled.
* Repository hostnames no longer need to be explicitly configured before
  use. (RBM-212)

Bug Fixes
---------
* Invalid user names are now reported correctly in the Repository Users
  plugin. (RBM-223)
